## ðŸ“¦ Getting Started

1. Clone the repository.
2. Now open the project in VS Code, then open the terminal in VS Code and type some commands.
3. Change the directory to Lexisg-frontend-intern-test.
4. After changing the directory through the terminal, type npm install to install the required dependencies for the project.
5. Run npm run dev to start the project on port 3000, and you're all set!

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/Lexisg-frontend-intern-test.git
cd Lexisg-frontend-intern-test
npm init
npm run dev  
